---
import Layout from '@layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms & Conditions - Building a Brand Online" description="Review the terms and conditions for using Building a Brand Online's website, courses, resources, and services. Understand your rights and responsibilities.">
  <div class="pt-32 pb-16 px-4 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8" style="font-family: 'Noto Sans Display', ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif;">Terms & Conditions</h1>
    <p class="text-[#666666]">Last updated: January 1, 2026</p>
    <div class="mt-8 space-y-6 text-[#666666] leading-relaxed">
      <p>By accessing and using Building a Brand Online's website and services, you accept and agree to be bound by these Terms and Conditions. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use our services.</p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1A1A1A] mt-8 mb-4">Use of Our Services</h2>
      <p>You agree to use our services only for lawful purposes and in accordance with these Terms. You are responsible for ensuring that your use of our services complies with all applicable laws, regulations, and ordinances.</p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1A1A1A] mt-8 mb-4">Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p>All content, materials, and resources available on our website, including but not limited to text, graphics, logos, images, and software, are the property of Building a Brand Online and are protected by applicable intellectual property laws.</p>
      
