      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1A1A1A] mt-8 mb-4">Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>Building a Brand Online shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, or consequential damages arising from your use of or inability to use our services, even if we have been advised of the possibility of such damages.</p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1A1A1A] mt-8 mb-4">Contact Information</h2>
      <p>For any questions about these Terms, please contact us at <a href="mailto:info@buildingabrandonline.com" class="text-[#4361EE] hover:underline">info@buildingabrandonline.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
